{{! About Us Section }}
<section class="bg-primary">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center text-light">
      <h2 class="section-title">Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        The Sustainability Cooperative at the University of Maryland, fondly known as SCoop,
        is a collective of student organizations, university departments, and community individuals
        interested in improving sustainability on campus. Founded by students in 2018, SCoop
        continues to grow and host more opportunities for members of our community and for the
        larger university and city. By joining together, we optimize funding opportunities, and
        individual SCoop member organizations gain an advantage in building interdisciplinary project
        teams. The cooperative meets regularly to network and workshop concepts and projects,
        allowing for increasing collaboration and innovation as well as elevated awareness of local initiatives!
      </p>
      <a href="#" type="" class="btn btn-outline-light mr-3"><span class="fas fa-user-plus icon-left"></span> Become a Member</a>
      <a href="#" type="" class="btn btn-outline-light"><span class="far fa-envelope icon-left"></span> Join Our Email List</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="bg-primary">
  <div class="container text-light">
    <div class="row text-center justify-content-center">
      <h2 class="section-title">What We Do</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      {{#each activities}}
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        {{>box title=title text=text}}
      </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

